<li><span class="citation" id="CITEREFAlphons1996">Alphons, K.J. (1996), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=Bd3sAAAAMAAJ"><i>Making a difference</i></a>, Penguin Books, <a href="Library_of_Congress_Control_Number" title="Library of Congress Control Number">LCCN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://lccn.loc.gov/96902754">96902754</a><span class="printonly">, <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=Bd3sAAAAMAAJ">http://books.google.com/books?id=Bd3sAAAAMAAJ</a></span></span></li>
</ul>
</div>
